  "original_title": "\u0db4\u0ddc\u0dc4\u0ddc\u0dbb \u0db1\u0dd0\u0dc0\u0dad\u0dca \u0db4\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0db8\u0dcf\u0daf\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Fertilizer stops late",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Agriculture and Wildlife Minister Mahinda Amaraweera says that the fertilizer ship that was supposed to arrive will also be delayed.",
        "The minister mentioned that the ship bringing 40,000 metric tons of fertilizer from Oman through the Government of India was scheduled to reach Sri Lanka today (5th), but due to the rough sea conditions, the arrival of the ship will be delayed until the 9th.",
        "The minister said this at the press conference to announce the cabinet decisions held at the Government Information Department."
      ],
